          "date": "2016-07-25 18:15:44.000000000",
          "tz": 0
        },
        "subject": "LU-7842 nfs: don't drop cap for getattr too",
        "message": "LU-7842 nfs: don't drop cap for getattr too\n\nThis is a follow up of LU-6528: ll_iget_for_nfs() ->\nsearch_inode_for_lustre() -> md_getattr() -> mdt_getattr() is a\npossible call trace in NFS export too, so mdt_getattr() should\nnot drop capability just like mdt_getattr_name() and\nmdt_intent_getattr().\n\nAlso rename mdt_init_ucred_intent_getattr() to\nmdt_init_ucred_getattr() to be more accurate.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I290acdcb73f0fab71b9c7ec274cfa2104a43e02c\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
